ADDITIONAL COMMENTS: TO PT: -You were admitted with chest pain. You were found to have a blockage in one of the arteries around your heart and this blockage was preventing your heart from getting enough oxygen. You underwent cardiac catheterization and a stent was placed to keep this blocked artery open.
